FBIS4-54469 "dreeu084_i_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-084 Daily Report 29 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA British Soldier Dies in Mine Explosion British Soldier Dies in Mine Explosion AU2904195994 Paris AFP in English 1954 GMT 29 Apr 94 AU2904195994 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] London, April 29 (AFP) -- A British soldier was killed and two injured when their Land-Rover went over an anti-tank mine in central Bosnia Friday [29 April], the Ministry of Defence said. The incident occurred near Gornji Vakuf, a ministry spokesman said. Also in the vehicle, on a routine reconnaissance mission, were three local guides, two of whom received minor injuries.
